{"title":"GPU manual for the poor","date":"2019-10-08T05:06:02.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 8, 2019","L":"10/08/2019","MM-DD":"10-08"},"link":"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor","tags":["server"],"updated":"2020-03-17T16:02:19.554Z","content":"<p>在资源紧张的情况下，除了要计划经济以外，我们还要计划gpu的使用。在此背景下，总结一份 gpu勤俭指南。</p>\n<h1 id=\"注意\">注意<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#注意\"></a></h1><p>运行程序前使用 CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=GPU编号 来指定使用哪块显卡，用多显卡的话在程序里写好，如果直接用 python **.py, 这样会占用全部显卡。</p>\n<h1 id=\"监控GPU状态\">监控GPU状态<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#监控GPU状态\"></a></h1><p>首先需要安装 gpustat 功能：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip  install gpustat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>查看gpu状态：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gpustat -u</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"指定使用GPU\">指定使用GPU<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#指定使用GPU\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"pytorch下：\">pytorch下：<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#pytorch下：\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li><p>直接在终端指定：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=<span class=\"number\">1</span> python my_script.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>pyton代码中指定：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"2\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>以上两种方式类似于tensorflow指定gpu的方式</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>使用set_device函数指定：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> torch</span><br><span class=\"line\">torch.cuda.set_device(id)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>ps: gpu编号从0开始</p>\n<h2 id=\"tensorflow下：\">tensorflow下：<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#tensorflow下：\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li>可在文件开头加入以下代码</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_DEVICE_ORDER\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"PCI_BUS_ID\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"1\"</span>       <span class=\"comment\"># 使用第二块GPU（从0开始）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>也可以指定使用某几块gpu</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_DEVICE_ORDER\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"PCI_BUS_ID\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"0, 2\"</span>    <span class=\"comment\"># 使用第一, 三块GPU</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>禁用GPU</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"-1\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"强制仅使用CPU\">强制仅使用CPU<a href=\"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor#强制仅使用CPU\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_DEVICE_ORDER\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\"PCI_BUS_ID\"</span>   <span class=\"comment\"># see issue #152</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">os.environ[<span class=\"string\">\"CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES\"</span>] = <span class=\"string\">\" \"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"连接打印机","link":"2019/10/08/连接打印机"},"next":{"title":"linux+python+virtual environment","link":"2019/10/08/Linux+python+virtual environment"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor/","toc":[{"title":"注意","id":"注意","index":"1"},{"title":"监控GPU状态","id":"监控GPU状态","index":"2"},{"title":"指定使用GPU","id":"指定使用GPU","index":"3","children":[{"title":"pytorch下：","id":"pytorch下：","index":"3.1"},{"title":"tensorflow下：","id":"tensorflow下：","index":"3.2"}]},{"title":"强制仅使用CPU","id":"强制仅使用CPU","index":"4"}],"reward":true}